item.title: Moving Away From Wordpress
item.description: Hello Everyone, I have decided this past weekend to final move completely away from WordPress for my blog; and I’m 100% excited for this transition! I have decided to use GitHub Pages for my new blog. I plan on migrating content to this new locaton, but in the meantime if you find any missing content that you have seen previously then please let me know and I will get it moved over ASAP.
